#MEM id=references source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/lena/skills/marketing-and-growth/email-sequence/references/email-types.md savings=4%
M|Emai|tx|A comprehensive guide to lifecycle and cg emails. Use this as an audit checklist and implementation reference.
M|Cont|it|Onboarding Emails (new us series, new cs series, key onboarding step reminder, new us invite)
M|Cont|it|Retention Emails (upgrade to paid, upgrade to higher plan, ask for rv, offer support proactively, pd usage rp, NPS survey, referral program)
M|Cont|it|Billing Emails (switch to annual, failed payment recovery, cancellation survey, upcoming renewal reminder)
M|Cont|it|Usage Emails (daily/weekly/monthly summary, key event or milestone notifications)
M|Cont|it|Win-Back Emails (expired trials, can cs)
M|Cont|it|cg Emails (monthly roundup/nl, seasonal promotions, pd updates, industry news roundup, pricing up)
M|Cont|it|em Audit Checklist (onboarding, retention, billing, usage, win-back, cg)
M|New |**Tr|us signs up (free or trial)
M|New |**Go|Activate us, drive to aha moment
M|New |**Ty|5-7 emails over 14 days
M|New |- Em|Welcome + single nx step (immediate)
M|New |- Em|Quick win / getting started (day 1)
M|New |- Em|Key feature highlight (day 3)
M|New |- Em|sc story / sl proof (day 5)
M|New |- Em|Check-in + offer help (day 7)
M|New |- Em|Advanced tip (day 10)
M|New |- Em|Upgrade pm or nx milestone (day 14)
M|New |**Ke|Activation rate, feature adoption
M|New |tx|---
M|New |**Tr|us converts to paid
M|New |**Go|Reinforce purchase decision, drive adoption, reduce early churn
M|New |**Ty|3-5 emails over 14 days
M|New |- Em|Thank you + what's nx (immediate)
M|New |- Em|Getting full value — setup checklist (day 2)
M|New |- Em|Pro tips for paid features (day 5)
M|New |- Em|sc story from similar cs (day 7)
M|New |- Em|Check-in + introduce support resources (day 14)
M|New |**Ke|Different from new us series—they've committed. Focus on reinforcement and expansion, not conversion.
